  "notes": [
    "Score scale is `[0, 1]` real, not the 0–100 display scale.",
    "Recency uses 180-day exponential decay; ageDays = (nowMs - recordCreatedAtMs) / 86_400_000.",
    "Authors without inbound vouches contribute zero weight, regardless of authorTrustScore.",
    "Flag penalties compound multiplicatively in array order; severity strings outside critical/serious/warning are ignored (info / future severities).",
    "Tombstone coordination penalty triggers at >= COORDINATION_TOMBSTONE_THRESHOLD (3) and applies once.",
    "Damping pulls every raw towards BASE_SCORE: overall = 0.85*raw + 0.15*0.1 → an empty-input subject lands near 0.21, not 0.",
    "Expected values are full IEEE-754 doubles (no rounding) — the reference function is deterministic so === comparison in the regression test is byte-exact."
  ]
